XML-Atom-Filter

XML::Atom::Filter eases creation of command line tools to filter and
process Atom feeds.

This release of XML::Atom::Filter provides real filtering ("grep") of
entries in addition to processing ("map") and fixes the documentation
for the atompost.pl example script.


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    * XML::Atom 0.11


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


